Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(178,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H33369F&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Edition\NThe 5 Riders in Full Force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Closed for the day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the sign, chief?\NYou're losing business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Keisuke! Take a look, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better get ready. Busy busy busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Summer Storytelling for Kids:\NAre the Kamen Riders Friend or Foe"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall now commence our\Ndiscussion of the Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lot of strapping young\Nchildren we have here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's starting! What about this\Nstoryteller? Cool moustache or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm sure we all agree that the\NKamen Riders are heroes, don't we? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...That's nothing but a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They've fooled you all just\Nto make themselves famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing but liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We all feel sorry for the\Npoor cyborgs, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These seem to be the villains of the piece,\Ndon't they? But it's just the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, the original Kamen Rider\Nis just a weakling with wads of cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With this in mind, it's natural to assume he\Nmust have bribed those monsters to take dives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rider #2 isn't much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He cuts a fine figure on\Nhis motorcycle, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But that too is a lie!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of Kamen Rider V3!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His transformation pose makes\Nhim look strong, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Deathtron taught him how to\Ndo it!! I shall demonstrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's with this storyteller!?\N-What's with this storyteller!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried keeping quiet, but I've\Nhad enough of your lies! Beat it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Liar!\N-The Kamen Riders are heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, get outta here!\N-Hold it, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone!\N...Stupid thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Without further ado, I present\Nthe true tale of the Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is gonna be the real thing!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began with the evil\Norganisation known as Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They kidnapped the young scientist Hongou\NTakeshi and transformed him into a cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...even trying to replace his love of\Npeace with their own wicked desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's group of scientists\Nhave modified your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to believe that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,E-even if I die... I won't obey you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hongou escaped and began his fight\Nagainst Shocker as the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou Takeshi transforms when\Nthe wind passes through his belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spider-Man, Sarracenian, the\NBee-Woman, and the Cobra-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokageron led Shocker's monsters\Ninto battle against Rider #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the killing shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won... The Rider Kick did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou Takeshi's allies included\NRuriko, Hiromi, Shirou, and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our second chapter introduces one\NI'm sure you know: Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When Rider #1 pursued Shocker to\NEurope, Ichimonji came to fill the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's real target...\Nmust be the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who'll protect Japan\Nin Hongou Takeshi's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cyborg too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce... the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty monsters like Pirasaurus\Nand Dokugander assailed Rider #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider #2 was assisted by Taki Kazuya, and Mari, Yuri,\NMichi and Hiromi of the Tachibana Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Rider #1, Hongou\NTakeshi, returned to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rider Kick!\N-Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Shocker stood no chance against\NHongou Takeshi and Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They defeated every monster which challenged them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You Kamen Riders might be able\Nto transform... But so can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Tailspin Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from its monsters, Shocker also sent\Nits strongest officers after the Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol, Dr. Death, and Ambassador\NHell appeared one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But even they were unable to best the Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Shocker's leader\Ncreated GelShocker to invade Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GelShocker was mighty, and\Nbacked Riders #1 and #2 into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I now declare GelShocker's\NJapanese branch in operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has absorbed Geldam's\Nresources... and become GelShocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am GelShocker's cyborg\NEagleMantis! All humans are my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away, and don't miss any!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to defeat the Riders, GelShocker\Nbuilt six fakes to confound them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ichimonji, now!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,G-GelShocker will have the last laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All glory to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...our great leader!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanquishing the most terrifying officer of all,\Nour heroes finally confronted Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up this plot for world conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see your real face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you two to hell with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with Shocker's leader vanquished, more\Nmonsters appeared before the two Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Namely: Scissors Jaguar, a soldier of Deathtron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, a certain man arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazami Shirou, whose family\Nwere executed by Deathtron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill #1 and #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Riders #1 and #2, he\Nwas reborn as Kamen Rider V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,#2, we've found our successor. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But the first two Riders sacrificed themselves to\Nprotect Tokyo from TurtleBazooka's atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform... V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, Kamen Rider\NV3 ran wild on his foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,V3 Screw Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,V3 Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Deathtron's leader\Nwouldn't surrender so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,High-ranking officers like Doktor G\Nand Baron Fang made their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,V3 Rolling Three-Stage Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fang Clan... perishes at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But for all these enemies, V3 gained an ally too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do you know who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riderman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right, Riderman!\NDeathtron scientist Yuuki Jouji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He modified himself for revenge\Nagainst Marshal Armour!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rope Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,V3, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Awoken to justice, Riderman\Nswore to fight alongside V3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Riderman ultimately departed for\Nthe heavens to protect peace on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Riderman... You did it.\NYou saved mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hero! From now on,\Nyou're Kamen Rider #4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, our tale climaxes with\Nthe most exciting scene of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With Riders #1, #2 and V3, Riderman miraculously alive, and the arrival of Rider X...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Five Riders were in full force at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Riders, Riders\NOh, Kamen Riders{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}They're never far away\NOur allies, the heroes of justice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Taking down the enemies of peace\NDon't give up, #1, #2, or V3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Don't give up, Kaizorg X Rider{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rider Double Kick!\N-Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to sit and\Nlisten to that fairy tale!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what happened and you know it!\NImagine thinking the Kamen Riders never lost!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the liar here! I thought\Nyou'd left already? Kick rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Waiting room{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it was something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, how the--!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's...\N-...two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, this guy's with GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, that's why you\Nwere lying about the Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no\Npoint me hiding now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The great King Dark has revived us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I try to pay the chief a visit\Nfor once, and... Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it, they're as bad as Deathtron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, this is Kazami Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while... since I ran wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get the kids out of here!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jin Keisuke. The\Nchief told me about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Kazami Shirou!\NExcuse me if I get a little wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kazami, look!\N-What? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform... V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've got V3's moves on\Nfilm as well as the X Rider's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kazami, good work!\N-You think so? Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've fully analysed\Nyour fighting style!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very much mistaken if you\Nthink you're the equal of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD have identified X's weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Kamen Rider X! Break\NGOD's hold and bring peace to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(10,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Spider Napoleon drains all of the X Rider's energy,\Nand only V3 - Kazami Shirou - can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He equips the X Rider with Mercury Power!\NX Rider gets even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Behold! X Rider's Great Transformation!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider